info.title: Cantata 140 - No. 2:  Er kommt, er kommt, der Braut'gam kommt!
info.author: J S Bach
info.comments: Some slight  attempt has been made to match this computer-generated version of this Work, as regards tempos, dynamics and orchestration, to an actual performance (though I forget which).  Other than that, it's just taken from the printed Breitkopf Score, with the piano reduction converted into strings and so on (as indicated), and the SATB Chorus voices represented by: piccolo, clarinet, french horn and bassoon
